_sText:
This is my first map GUNGAME and it takes place into a big cardboard box. 

It is a pretty simplistic map. 

- There are ladders to climb on containers and crates.
- There are two mains alleys and two side paths.
- There are 22 spawns for CT an T so the map is playable on a 44 slots server.
- The box's wall are made of a custom texture.
- The metal crates are made with .Eric metal texture pack
- The skybox is made by komaokc

And I think that is all !
